quity and retirement plan marketing at ubs investment advisors where he played a leading role in the rebranding of the employer plans advisory services corporate equity business as senior vice president of retirement products at citi personal wealth management john was responsible for the overhaul and relaunch of the brokerdealer’s defined contribution plan product platform and leading a team to ensure compliance with regulations a and b at oppenheimerfunds he led the execution of the awardwinning national branding campaign globalize your thinking prior to that he managed oppenheimerfunds’ small business and individual retirement plans product and marketing team in that role he managed the development of one of the first montecarlobased retirement income planning tools for financial advisors and was a frequent public speaker on the topics of retirement income and retirement distribution strategies john attended st olaf college and holds a bachelor of arts degree in economics this link directs you to a thirdparty website dreyfus accepts no responsibility for content on these thirdparty sites or for the services provided also please be aware that when you use services provided by one of these thirdparty sites youre subject to that sites terms of service and privacy policy rules ie sharing of personal information which you should review carefully before proceeding yes no pershing wins for best new highnetworth hnw product united states global sites united states europe middle east  africa global locations all locations the americas europe middle east  africa asia pacific toggle navigationmenu what we provide solutions at a glance clearing custody and settlement investment solutions managed investments solutions marketing and practice management prime services retirement solutions technology and enterprise data management trading services wealth solutions events the revolutionary platform and complete solution for advisors who we serve advisors alternative investment ma